&lt;p&gt;An exciting integration post for an Occupational Therapist to join our team in Kerrier.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To provide assessment and rehabilitation in to patients in the community setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will come across a wide range of clinical conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work in a Multidisciplinary team, working alongside, Nurses, Physiotherapists, STEPS workers and Generic Support Workers and will link with the wider Integration teams, voluntary sector, social services and Community Rehabilitation Team .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for 28 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
